LICENSE — PLACEHOLDER, NOT YET FINALIZED
==========================================

Cerebrum's licensing terms have not yet been selected by the project's
governing organization (see docs/architecture/specification/00_Project_Charter.md
for project ownership context).

This placeholder exists so that:

  1. Every clone of this repository is explicit that no license grant is
     currently in effect — this code is All Rights Reserved by default
     under copyright law until a license is chosen and this file is replaced.
  2. Tooling that expects a LICENSE file to exist (package registries,
     OSS scanners, contributor tooling) does not silently assume an
     unintended license.

ACTION REQUIRED BEFORE PUBLIC RELEASE OR EXTERNAL DISTRIBUTION:

  - The Architecture Owner (docs/architecture/specification/109_Project_Governance.md)
    and project leadership must select a license (e.g., a proprietary
    commercial license, or an open-source license such as Apache-2.0 or
    MIT if any component is intended for open distribution) and replace
    this file with the actual license text.
  - Until that decision is made, this repository and its contents should
    be treated as proprietary and confidential.

This file is intentionally NOT a real license. Do not remove this notice
without replacing it with an actual, reviewed license grant.
